<?xml version="1.0" ?>
<dialog name="Catherine" displayName="Catherine Willows">
	<conversation location="CatherinesOffice" visit="1" name="1">
		<statement num="1"><![CDATA[Hi, thanks for coming by to help.

There was a fire, possibly arson, at a local home. A young man was killed.]]></statement>
		<statement num="2"><![CDATA[We don't know yet. Apparently, one person escaped the fire.]]></statement>
		<statement num="3"><![CDATA[Sara is already at the scene; she might need a hand.

You'll need your smartphone, a camera and a fire scene tool kit.]]></statement>
		<statement num="4"><![CDATA[It's on my desk.]]></statement>
		<statement num="5"><![CDATA[You can relocate to the crime scene by using the locations tab on the bottom of the screen.]]></statement>
		<response num="1"><![CDATA[What happened?]]></response>
		<response num="2"><![CDATA[How can I help?]]></response>
		<response num="3"><![CDATA[How do I get my gear?]]></response>
		<response num="4"><![CDATA[How do I get to the crime scene?]]></response>
		<response num="5"><![CDATA[I'll pick up my gear and head to the crime scene.]]></response>
	</conversation>
</dialog>